  m_text: 'Each enemy drops gems that you can collect and use for progression.



    Chests
    refill over time. Once ready, destroy them to get a large amount of gems.



    Carry
    gems to the Statue Of Nexus to secure them. If you die before depositing, you
    may lose progress.




'
